comments: As Doncic (DAL) and VanVleet (HOU) engage off-ball, marginal contact occurs when Doncic releases toward the incoming pass.

Kleber (DAL) moves alongside Smith Jr.'s (HOU) path and absorbs the contact when Smith Jr. changes direction toward the end of his drive. Marginal contact occurs before Smith Jr.'s upward shooting motion.
Green (HOU) trails behind Irving (DAL) and lightly brushes Irving's body during his layup attempt.
Bullock Jr. (HOU) establishes himself in Exum's (DAL) path, and marginal contact occurs to Exum's hip as Bullock Jr. releases his screening position.
Smith Jr. (HOU) moves alongside Exum (DAL) during his drive and absorbs the contact.

Replay review of the foul called on Exum (DAL) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Exum (DAL) extends his hand into VanVleet's (HOU) chest, and the contact affects VanVleet's SQBR and occurs prior to any head contact.
Doncic (DAL) absorbs the initial contact with Holiday (HOU) before marginal lower-body contact occurs as Holiday moves around the screen.
Holiday (HOU) contests Irving's (DAL) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Washington (DAL) and Bullock (HOU) both lunge toward the rebound when incidental contact occurs as Bullock secures the loose ball.
VanVleet (HOU) avoids stepping out of bounds while still in possession of the ball.
Jones Jr. (DAL) briefly places his hand on Smth Jr.'s (HOU) side as they engage and separate off-ball.
Exum (DAL) has his arm out in front of VanVleet (HOU) as they engage when they move in the same direction toward the sideline before VanVleet retrieves the inbound pass.
Jones Jr. (DAL) commits a take foul on Smith Jr. (HOU) near the baseline.
Bullock Jr. (HOU) reaches for the ball when marginal contact occurs with Exum (DAL) as he gathers the pass in the backcourt.
After Exum's (DAL) handoff, he turns away from Brooks (HOU) and slips the contact when their bodies graze.
After communicating with the Replay Center, it is confirmed Exum (DAL) released his shot attempt prior to the clock expiring.
VanVleet (HOU) steps slightly forward towards Irving's (DAL) path, and the contact during the drive is marginal.
Smith Jr. (HOU) jumps alongside Irving's (DAL) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Doncic (DAL) is turning away from Brooks' (HOU) path, and the contact during the driving shot attempt is marginal.
Smith Jr. (HOU) contests Exum's (DAL) shot near the rim, and the contact after the release is marginal.
Kleber (DAL) jumps vertically and absorbs the contact from Green (HOU) during the driving shot attempt.
Brooks (HOU) brings his hand forward towards Doncic's (DAL) front, and the contact on the perimeter is marginal.
Smith Jr. (HOU) straddles the lane line and is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Smith Jr. (HOU) establishes himself in Washington's (DAL) path and absorbs the contact.
Jones Jr. (DAL) contests Green's (HOU) driving shot attempt, and the contact with Green's outstretched leg is marginal.
Jones Jr. (DAL) makes contact with the ball after the ball touches the backboard and has a chance to score.
VanVleet (HOU) and Doncic (DAL) come together at the same spot on the perimeter, and the contact is marginal.
Brooks (HOU) brings his hand forward towards Doncic's (DAL) arm, and the contact during the drive is marginal.
Doncic (DAL) cleanly blocks Smith Jr.'s (HOU) jump shot attempt.
Doncic (DAL) cleanly deflects the ball away from Brooks (HOU), and the ensuing arm contact is incidental.
Holiday (HOU) brings his arm toward Irving's (DAL) path, and the contact during the drive is marginal.
Brooks (HOU) brings his forearm towards Exum's (DAL) upper body, and the contact during the drive is marginal.
Smith Jr. (HOU) brushes Doncic's (DAL) arm at the start of his drive.
Holiday (HOU) brings his hand towards Doncic's (DAL) lower body, and the contact during the driving shot attempt is marginal.
